[[Image:Buffalo.jpg|thumb|right|200 px|A buffalo]]

# Any of the Old World mammals of the family Bovidae, such as the Cape Buffalo, ''Syncerus caffer'', or the water buffalo.
# A related North American animal, the American Bison, ''Bison bison''.  [[Image:Bison.jpg|thumb|right|300 px|A couple of bison (Noun definition 2) relaxing]]
# A buffalo robe.
# The [[buffalo fish]].
# A bison erroneously called buffalo, (''historically various'') ''Bison bison'', ''Bos Americanus'' or ''Bisonte americano''.

